	<content:encoded><![CDATA[      One of the major changes in FarCry 6.0 (codenamed: Formailty) is the move to the exclusive use of JQuery and JQuery UI in the Webtop.&nbsp; JQuery UI is being used as the standard for all the UI elements - well at least that is the direction we're headed.&nbsp; Some parts of the Webtop chrome will retain the original blue/grey "Glamour" release design.<p />  The default UI theme we're using in the beta is a Silver/Grey called "Smoothness" -- it's unobtrusive and works well.<p />  <p />  <p />  <p />  Have you got a better colour scheme in mind? Try your hand at theme building and let us know: <a href="http://jqueryui.com/themeroller/" class="moz-txt-link-freetext">http://jqueryui.com/themeroller/</a><br />   <p><div class='p_embed p_image_embed'>
